TOEIC Analyst is designed to prepare students for the TOEIC through analysis of common TOEIC question types and strategies for approaching each question. This book contains more than 700 questions in total to allow students to practice techniques for quickly recognizing test tasks and avoiding common mistakes.Tips for analyzing various question types commonly found on TOEIC testsExercises for students to practice each question typeSample tests at the end of each section focusing on specific listening or reading skills for further practiceTwo complete practice tests designed to simulate actual TOEIC tests including layout and directions as found on the TOEIC testComplete audio recordings, transcripts, and answer key 
