1. Baskı
The English You Need for Business +Cd
https://imageserver.kitapyurdu.com/select.php?imageid=1141038&width=500&isWatermarked=true
2014-01-01
 55,56
The English You Need for Business introduces vocabulary for talking about daily processes in an office.The English You Need for Business highlights verbs-words for doing or acting. With a larger vocabulary of verbs, you can more clearly speak or write about what happens in your life. The pictures make it easy for you to see what the new vocabulary means.The Picture Process approach allows a lively and flexible presentation of the basic vocabulary of topics like making a presentation, following up after a sales visit and having a business lunch. Students both in class and for self-study will find the picture process approach efficient and effective.
